<h1>This is the dashboard. It is used to make sure it is connected to the rest
  of the files. Handlebars is confusing, and I hope I figure it out soon. I also
  want to see if I like this keyboard. Do you have any suggestions for a good
  keyboard?</h1>

<h2>Your comments</h2>
<ul>
  {{#each comments}}
    <li>{{this.comment_text}}</li>
  {{/each}}
</ul>

<form action="/dashboard/posts/comments" method="POST">
  <textarea name="comment_text" placeholder="Post comment"></textarea>
  <button type="submit">Post</button>
</form>

{{#if query.logout}}
  <p>Successfully logged out!</p>
  <a href="/login">Login</a>
  <a href="/signup">Sign up</a>
{{else}}
  {{#if logged_in}}
    <p>User created successfully!</p>
    <a href="/logout" id="logout">Logout</a>
  {{else}}
    <a href="/login">Login</a>
    <a href="/signup">Sign up</a>
  {{/if}}
{{/if}}
